{"word":"G2481 - ἴσως - ísōs - ee'-soce - It may be","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἴσως</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ísōs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ee'-soce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">It may be</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அதுபோல, ஆகிலும் - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"1. equally, in like manner"},{"paragraph":"2. agreeably to expectation"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Adverb from <a href=\"#/G2470 - ἴσος - ísos - ee'-sos/2470\">G2470</a>; <i>likely</i>, that is, <i>perhaps:</i> - it may be.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}